---
/**
 * GroupFooterNav Component
 *
 * Renders a responsive grid container for footer navigation groups.
 * - Uses a single column layout on small screens and two columns on medium screens and above.
 * - Accepts child elements via the default slot.
 * - Applies spacing between grid items and ensures the container height fits its content.
 *
 * Usage:
 * Place navigation links or groups inside the component to display them in a structured grid layout.
 */
---

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 h-max">
    <slot />
</div>
